page.title: 20Acknowledgements
page.content: THe survey was carried out and the reports written by members of Cumnor Women's Institute who acknowledge help and encouragement given by their families and friends and by residents in the area. Photographs were taken by the President of Cumnor Women's Institute, Mrs.M.Drury and her husband Mr.E.Drury The group records its thanks to Mr.Jolyon Booth, Head of Computing at Radley College, without whose help the survey could not have been undertaken, and to the College for permitting the use of the computer.
